# ── Secrets & key material — NEVER commit ──────────────────────────────
# The wallet writes its encrypted keystore into the runtime data dir.
# Even though keys are encrypted at rest, an encrypted keystore is still
# personal key material and must never leave the machine via git.
data/
keystore.json
*.keystore
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
# Anything that looks like a raw private key dump or seed backup
*privkey*
*private-key*
*seed*.txt
mnemonic*.txt

# Environment / credentials
.env
.env.*
*.local
secrets.json
credentials.json

# ── Dependencies (reinstalled with `npm install`) ──────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ── Build artifacts / caches ───────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
build/
out/
.next/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo
.cache/

# ── OS / editor noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# NOTE: brand/ and design/ images (PNG/SVG) are intentionally tracked —
# the README hero + screenshots reference them. Do not add a global *.png ignore.
